member.name: T:SvcEvents.EventsClient
member.summary: Includes methods for managing Project Server event handler associations. Read the list of Project Server events, event handler associations for a specific event, or all event handler associations. Create, update, and delete event handler associations.

member.name: M:SvcEvents.EventsClient.CreateEventHandlerAssociations(SvcEvents.EventHandlersDataSet)
member.summary: Associates Project Server events with event handlers.
member.param: DataSet with list of events and event handlers to associate.

member.name: M:SvcEvents.EventsClient.DeleteEventHandlerAssociations(System.Guid[])
member.summary: Deletes Project Server event handler associations.
member.param: Array of event handler GUIDs.

member.name: M:SvcEvents.EventsClient.ReadEventHandlerAssociation(System.Guid)
member.summary: Gets the information for a specified Project Server event handler.
member.returns: The EventHandlersDataSet contains information about the specified event handler association, including the event handler assembly name, class name, description, related event, and order in which the event handler is called (the sequence number).
member.param: GUID of the event handler.

member.name: M:SvcEvents.EventsClient.ReadEventHandlerAssociations
member.summary: Gets information about all of the event handlers for all Project Server events.
member.returns: The EventHandlersDataSet contains information about all of the event handler associations for all events, including the event handler assembly name, class name, description, related event, and order in which the event handler is called (the sequence number).

member.name: M:SvcEvents.EventsClient.ReadEventHandlerAssociationsForEvent(SvcEvents.PSEventID)
member.summary: Gets information about all of the event handlers for a specified Project Server event.
member.returns: The EventHandlersDataSet contains information about all of the event handler associations for a specified event, including the event handler assembly names, class names, descriptions, the related event, and order in which each event handler is called (the sequence number).
member.param: GUID of the event.

member.name: M:SvcEvents.EventsClient.ReadEventsList
member.summary: Gets a list of Project Server events.
member.returns: The EventsDataSet includes the event ID, event name, and source of the event.

member.name: M:SvcEvents.EventsClient.UpdateEventHandlerAssociations(SvcEvents.EventHandlersDataSet)
member.summary: Updates one or more event handler associations.
member.param: DataSet with list of events and event handlers to associate.
